==Description==
The '''Icy Rock''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Icy Rock has a value of 2 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Icy appears in the Underground as a 4x4 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:IcyRockMine 0-7-3.png|100px]] 

==Acquisition==
Icy Rocks can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

